<activity xml:id="act-hacerUnRectangulo" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>Hagamos un rectángulo</title>

<statement>
  <p>Tu profesor te dará un poco de cinta. Úsala para crear un rectángulo que tenga el área que le asignaron a tu grupo.</p>

<p>Área 1: 4 pies cuadrados</p>
<p>Área 2: 6 pies cuadrados</p>
<p>Área 3: 9 pies cuadrados</p>
<p>Área 4: 10 pies cuadrados</p>
<p>Área 5: 12 pies cuadrados</p>
<p>Área 6: 16 pies cuadrados</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Students show rectangles with the following side lengths:</p>
<ul>
      <li>Area 1: 1 foot by 4 feet, or 2 feet by 2 feet</li>
      <li>Area 2: 1 foot by 6 feet, or 2 feet by 3 feet</li>
      <li>Area 3: 1 foot by 9 feet, or 3 feet by 3 feet</li>
      <li>Area 4: 1 foot by 10 feet, or 2 feet by 5 feet</li>
      <li>Area 5: 1 foot by 12 feet, 2 feet by 6 feet, or 3 feet by 4 feet</li>
      <li>Area 6: 1 foot by 16 feet, 2 feet by 8 feet, or 4 feet by 4 feet</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


